<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Notre Garderie - Où les Jeunes Esprits S'Épanouissent</title>
    <!-- <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script> -->
    <script src="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/lottie-web/5.12.2/lottie.min.js"></script>
    <link href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.0.0/css/all.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    {%load static%}
    {%load tailwind_tags %}
    {% tailwind_css %}
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="{%static 'style/home.css'%}">
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        'lime': {
                            50: '#f7fee7',
                            100: '#ecfccb',
                            200: '#d9f99d',
                            300: '#bef264',
                            400: '#a3e635',
                            500: '#84cc16',
                            600: '#65a30d',
                            700: '#4d7c0f',
                            800: '#3f6212',
                            900: '#365314'
                        }
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'fade-in-up': 'fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards',
                        'fade-in-left': 'fadeInLeft 0.8s ease-out forwards',
                        'fade-in-right': 'fadeInRight 0.8s ease-out forwards',
                        'bounce-gentle': 'bounceGentle 2s ease-in-out infinite',
                        'float': 'float 3s ease-in-out infinite',
                        'pulse-soft': 'pulseSoft 2s ease-in-out infinite',
                    },

                }
            }

        }
    </script>
    <script src="https://cdn.lordicon.com/lordicon.js"></script>
    <style>
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'Viga';
            src: url('{% static "fonts/Viga-Regular.ttf" %}') format('truetype');
        }
        @font-face {
            font-family: 'RadioCanada';
            src: url('{% static "fonts/RadioCanada-VariableFont.ttf" %}') format('truetype');
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="bg-white overflow-x-hidden">


<!-- Navigation -->
<nav class="fixed top-0 w-full bg-white/90 backdrop-blur-sm z-50 shadow-sm">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 py-3">
        <div class="flex justify-between items-center">
            <!-- Logo and Brand -->
            <div class="flex items-center space-x-2 flex-shrink-0">
                <img src="{% static 'images/ambassadors_logo.png' %}" alt="Logo Ambassador's" class="w-12 h-12 sm:w-16 sm:h-16">
                <h1 class="text-lime-700 font-bold text-lg sm:text-xl lg:text-2xl"><span class="invisible lg:visible">The Ambassador's</span> Daycare</h1>
            </div>

            <!-- Desktop Navigation -->
            <div class="hidden lg:flex space-x-6 xl:space-x-8">
                <a href="#about" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors text-sm xl:text-base">À Propos</a>
                <a href="#approach" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors text-sm xl:text-base">Notre Approche</a>
                <a href="#activities" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors text-sm xl:text-base">Activités</a>
                <a href="#environment" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors text-sm xl:text-base">Environnement</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors text-sm xl:text-base">Contact</a>
            </div>

            <!-- Language Dropdown (Desktop) -->
            <div class="hidden lg:flex items-center space-x-2">
                <div class="relative">
                    <button class="bg-lime-500 hover:bg-lime-600 text-white px-3 py-2 xl:px-4 xl:py-2 rounded-full shadow-lg font-semibold flex items-center transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:scale-105 text-sm xl:text-base" onclick="toggleLanguageDropdown()">
                        <i class="fas fa-globe text-xs xl:text-sm mr-1 xl:mr-2"></i>
                        <span class="hidden xl:inline">Language</span>
                        <span class="xl:hidden">Lang</span>
                        <i class="fas fa-chevron-down ml-1 xl:ml-2 transition-transform duration-300 text-xs" id="langDropdownIcon"></i>
                    </button>

                    <div class="absolute top-full right-0 mt-2 w-48 bg-white rounded-xl shadow-xl border border-gray-200 opacity-0 transform scale-95 transition-all duration-300 origin-top-right z-50" id="languageDropdown">
                        <div class="py-2">
                            <a href="{% url 'daycare:home' %}" class="flex items-center px-4 py-3 hover:bg-lime-50 transition-colors duration-200 group">
                                <img src="{% static 'images/UK.svg' %}" alt="English" class="w-6 h-4 mr-3 rounded-sm">
                                <div>
                                    <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-lime-600">English</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Switch to English</div>
                                </div>
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-right ml-auto text-gray-400 group-hover:text-lime-600"></i>
                            </a>
                            <div class="border-t border-gray-100"></div>
                            <a href="{% url 'daycare:home_fr' %}" class="flex items-center px-4 py-3 hover:bg-orange-50 transition-colors duration-200 group">
                                <img src="{% static 'images/french_langage.png' %}" alt="Français" class="w-6 h-4 mr-3 rounded-sm">
                                <div>
                                    <div class="font-semibold text-gray-800 group-hover:text-orange-600">Français</div>
                                    <div class="text-sm text-gray-500">Basculer en français</div>
                                </div>
                                <i class="fas fa-chevron-right ml-auto text-gray-400 group-hover:text-orange-600"></i>
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Mobile Menu Button -->
            <div class="lg:hidden flex items-center space-x-2">
                <!-- Mobile Language Button -->
                <button class="bg-lime-500 hover:bg-lime-600 text-white p-4 rounded-full shadow-lg transition-all duration-300" onclick="toggleMobileLanguage()">
                    <i class="fas fa-globe text-xl"></i>
                </button>

                <!-- Hamburger Menu Button -->
                <button id="mobile-menu-btn" class="text-lime-700 p-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50 transition-colors">
                    <svg class="w-6 h-6" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                        <path class="hamburger-line-1" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 6h16"></path>
                        <path class="hamburger-line-2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 12h16"></path>
                        <path class="hamburger-line-3" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M4 18h16"></path>
                    </svg>
                </button>
            </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Mobile Menu -->
        <div id="mobile-menu" class="lg:hidden hidden bg-white border-t border-gray-200 mt-3 pt-4 pb-4 rounded-b-lg shadow-lg">
            <div class="flex flex-col space-y-4">
                <a href="#about" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">À Propos</a>
                <a href="#approach" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">Notre Approche</a>
                <a href="#activities" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">Activités</a>
                <a href="#environment" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">Environnement</a>
                <a href="#contact" class="text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">Contact</a>

                <!-- Mobile Language Options -->
                <div class="border-t border-gray-200 pt-4 mt-4" id="mobile-language-options" style="display: none;">
                    <h4 class="text-sm font-semibold text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider px-4 mb-2">Langue</h4>
                    <a href="{% url 'daycare:home' %}" class="flex items-center text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">
                        <img src="{% static 'images/UK.svg' %}" alt="English" class="w-5 h-3 mr-3 rounded-sm">
                        English
                    </a>
                    <a href="{% url 'daycare:home_fr' %}" class="flex items-center text-lime-700 hover:text-lime-500 transition-colors px-4 py-2 rounded-lg hover:bg-lime-50">
                        <img src="{% static 'images/french_langage.png' %}" alt="Français" class="w-5 h-3 mr-3 rounded-sm">
                        Français
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</nav>

<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="gradient-bg min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-4 pt-20 xl:pt-0 xl:mt-12 max-w-screen overflow-break">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="text-center lg:text-left">
                <div class="hero-text-container">
                    <h1 class="text-5xl lg:text-7xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6">
                        <span class="hero-line-1 opacity-0">Bienvenue Dans Notre</span>
                        <span class="hero-line-2 text-lime-600 block opacity-0">Garderie</span>
                    </h1>
                    <p class="text-xl text-lime-700 mb-8 hero-subtitle opacity-0">
                        <span class="typewriter-text" data-text="Un environnement aimant où commence le parcours de votre enfant"></span>
                    </p>
                </div>

                <div class="hero-features space-y-4 mb-8 opacity-0">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start hero-feature-1">
                        <i class="fas fa-baby text-lime-600 mr-3 bounce-icon"></i>
                        <span class="text-lg text-lime-800">Enfants de 6 mois à 3 ans</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-center lg:justify-start hero-feature-2">
                        <i class="fas fa-clock text-lime-600 mr-3 bounce-icon"></i>
                        <span class="text-lg text-lime-800">Ouvert du lundi au vendredi : 8h30 - 16h00</span>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <button class="hero-cta bg-lime-500 hover:bg-lime-600 text-white px-8 py-4 sm:px-10 sm:py-5 rounded-full text-lg sm:text-xl font-bold transition-all duration-300 opacity-0 shadow-2xl" style="font-family: 'Viga';">
                    <i class="fas fa-heart mr-2 pulse-heart"></i>
                    <span class="cta-text">Rejoignez Notre Famille</span>
                </button>

            </div>
            <div class="flex justify-center hero-image opacity-0 rounded-xl xl:rounded-none">
                <img src="{% static 'images/BeFunky-collage-welcome-daycare.png' %}" alt="Bienvenue à la Garderie Ambassador's" class="rounded-xl shadow-xl xl:rounded-none xl:shadow-none floating-image">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>


<!-- About Section -->
<section id="about" class="py-10 mt-0 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6">À Propos de Notre Garderie</h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-lime-500 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <img src="{% static 'images/BeFunky-collage-goal-daycare.png' %}" alt="Groupe Scolaire Bilingue Laïc Les Ambassadeurs" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-2xl">
            </div>
            <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <h3 class="text-2xl lg:text-3xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6">Avec Amour & Passion, Nous Bâtissons les Leaders de Demain</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Dans notre garderie, nous croyons que chaque enfant est un futur leader qui mérite d'être nourri dès le départ avec de fortes valeurs et de bonnes manières. Nous créons une fondation qui aide les enfants à devenir des membres précieux de notre société.
                </p>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-8 leading-relaxed">
                    Notre environnement spacieux et accueillant est conçu pour la sécurité, le bonheur et le développement de votre enfant. Dès son arrivée, votre enfant fait partie d'une communauté aimante où l'apprentissage se fait naturellement par le jeu et la découverte.
                </p>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-6">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-lime-50 rounded-lg card-hover">
                        <i class="fas fa-users text-3xl text-lime-600 mb-3"></i>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lime-800">Communauté</h4>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-lime-50 rounded-lg card-hover">
                        <i class="fas fa-shield-alt text-3xl text-lime-600 mb-3"></i>
                        <h4 class="font-semibold text-lime-800">Sécurité d'Abord</h4>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Approach Section -->
<section id="approach" class="py-20 gradient-bg">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6">Notre Approche & Philosophie</h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-lime-600 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
            <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <h3 class="text-3xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6 ">Apprendre par le Jeu</h3>
                <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
                    Nous comprenons que les enfants de 6 mois à 3 ans sont naturellement attirés par le jeu, c'est pourquoi notre approche tout entière est centrée sur l'apprentissage par le jeu.
                </p>
                <div class="bg-white p-6 rounded-xl shadow-lg mb-6 card-hover">
                    <h4 class="text-xl font-semibold text-lime-800 mb-3">Qu'est-ce qui nous rend uniques ?</h4>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
                        Notre capacité à intégrer de manière transparente les compétences essentielles au développement, notamment les habiletés motrices précoces, les activités préparatoires à l'écriture et le développement du langage, dans des expériences ludiques attrayantes et adaptées à l'âge des enfants.
                    </p>
                </div>
                <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4">
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg card-hover">

                        <lord-icon
                                src="{%static 'images/exercise.json'%}"
                                trigger="loop"
                                stroke="regular"
                                state="hover-roll"
                                colors="primary:#bcee66,secondary:#0a5c15"
                                style="width:5rem; height:5rem ;">
                        </lord-icon>

                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lime-800">Motricité</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg card-hover">
                        <lord-icon
                                src="{%static 'images/edit.json'%}"
                                trigger="loop"
                                stroke="regular"
                                state="hover-roll"
                                colors="primary:#bcee66,secondary:#0a5c15"
                                style="width:5rem; height:5rem ;">
                        </lord-icon>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lime-800">Préparation à Écriture</p>
                    </div>
                    <div class="text-center p-4 bg-white rounded-lg card-hover">
                        <lord-icon
                                src="{%static 'images/conversation.json'%}"
                                trigger="loop"
                                stroke="regular"
                                state="hover-roll"
                                colors="primary:#bcee66,secondary:#0a5c15"
                                style="width:5rem; height:5rem ;">
                        </lord-icon>
                        <p class="text-sm font-semibold text-lime-800">Langage</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="animate-on-scroll rounded-xl lg:rounded-lg">
                <img src="{% static 'images/BeFunky-collage-approach-daycare.png' %}" alt="Groupe Scolaire Bilingue Laïc Les Ambassadeurs" class="w-full rounded-xl shadow-xl xl:rounded-lg ">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Activities Section -->
<section id="activities" class="py-20 bg-white">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6">Vie Quotidienne & Activités</h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-lime-500 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Chaque journée est soigneusement structurée pour offrir un équilibre parfait entre apprentissage, jeu, repos et soins
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-16">
            <div class="bg-lime-50 p-6 rounded-xl card-hover animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-sun text-4xl text-orange-500 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-lime-800">Activités Matinales</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Arrivée en douceur & lecture</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Activités fonctionnelles</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Expression créative</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl card-hover animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-palette text-4xl text-lime-600 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-lime-800">Temps Créatif</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Peinture & coloriage</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Activités de dessin</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Arts & travaux manuels</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-lime-50 p-6 rounded-xl card-hover animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-music text-4xl text-orange-500 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-lime-800">Langage & Musique</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Chansons & chant</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Heure de conte</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Développement du langage</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl card-hover animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-utensils text-4xl text-lime-600 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-lime-800">Repas</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Déjeuner ensemble</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Collations des jours cinéma</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-lime-50 p-6 rounded-xl card-hover animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-bed text-4xl text-orange-500 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-lime-800">Temps de Repos</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Sieste paisible</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Activités calmes</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Réveil en douceur</li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            <div class="bg-orange-50 p-6 rounded-xl card-hover animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="text-center mb-4">
                    <i class="fas fa-seedling text-4xl text-lime-600 mb-3"></i>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-lime-800">Compétences de Vie</h3>
                </div>
                <ul class="space-y-2 text-gray-700">
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Lavage des mains</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Ranger</li>
                    <li><i class="fas fa-check text-lime-600 mr-2"></i>Bonnes manières</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>


    </div>
</section>

<!-- Environment Section -->
<section id="environment" class="py-20 gradient-bg">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4">
        <div class="text-center mb-16 animate-on-scroll">
            <h2 class="text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-6">Notre Environnement</h2>
            <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-lime-600 mx-auto mb-8"></div>
            <p class="text-xl text-gray-700 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Des espaces sûrs, stimulants et accueillants conçus pour la découverte et la croissance
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center mb-16">
            <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <div class="bg-white p-8 rounded-xl shadow-lg card-hover hover:border-orange-800 hover:border-2 hover:border-dashed">
                    <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-lime-800 mb-4">
                        <i class="fas fa-home text-lime-600 mr-3"></i>
                        Espace Intérieur
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
                        Un environnement éducatif spacieux enrichi de décorations colorées et engageantes qui créent une atmosphère chaleureuse et stimulante pour l'apprentissage et le jeu. Chaque coin suscite la curiosité tout en offrant sécurité et confort.
                    </p>
                    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4">
                        <div class="text-center p-3 bg-lime-50 rounded-lg">
                            <lord-icon
                                    src="{%static 'images/puzzle.json'%}"
                                    trigger="hover"
                                    stroke="bold"
                                    state="hover-roll"
                                    colors="primary:#e88c30,secondary:#5c330a"
                                    style="width:5rem; height:5rem ;">
                            </lord-icon>
                            <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Zones d'Apprentissage</p>
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-center p-3 bg-lime-50 rounded-lg">
                            <div class="text-center p-3 bg-lime-50 rounded-lg">
                                <lord-icon
                                        src="{%static 'images/comfort.json'%}"
                                        trigger="hover"
                                        stroke="bold"
                                        state="hover-roll"
                                        colors="primary:#e88c30,secondary:#5c330a"
                                        style="width:5rem; height:5rem ;">
                                </lord-icon>
                                <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Zones de Confort</p>
                            </div>

                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <div class="animate-on-scroll">
                <!-- Replace with indoor environment image -->
                <img src="{% static 'images/BeFunky-collage-indoor2-daycare.png' %}" alt="Groupe Scolaire Bilingue Laïc Les Ambassadeurs" class="w-full rounded-xl">
